      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Economics (Arts)              : Microeconomic theories of economic development and empirical evidence on population, labour, firms, poverty. Inequality and environment.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014, Winter 2015          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
